rows.label: qst005101_msg0001
rows.name:
That damn Akatsuki... I never did like
the guy, acting all high and mighty
even though he's just a Blade...

rows.label: qst005101_msg0002
rows.name:
And now he's letting miscreants get
away so we can clean them up instead?

rows.label: qst005101_msg0003
rows.name:
That does it. After I get rid of you guys,
I'm taking him down next!
